      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIL HEAVENS ROCKN NZ (7) has the hoof on the till after placing in his last three outings at this circuit and distance, missing by less than 2m in a  higher-graded race last week. Gets a soft run on the inside of the second line and if he gets the gaps can break through. BETTING STAR (1) was runner-up here two starts back and did a good job again at her latest appearance for third at Bathurst. Looks close to a win and should enjoy the favours from the ace draw. ROYAL VINCENT (2) was far from disgraced when fifth from a tough barrier at his most recent appearance. Led to win here three back so is much better served by this draw. GOODTIME BRAVO (9) may need some luck from this draw but deserves respect after missing by a nose here last week.",
